x^2-2=\frac{x^2}{2}+\frac{x^2}{2}-2\ge \frac{x^2}{2}
x\ge 2
x\ge 1
2x+1\le 3x
x\ge 2
\frac{x^2-2}{2x+1} \ge \frac{x^2/2}{3x}=\frac{x}{6}.
x\gt \max(2, 6K)
\frac{x^2-2}{2x+1}\gt K
\frac{x^2-2}{2x+1}\lt K
x\gt -1/2
x\lt -1/2
K-\sqrt{K^2+K+2} \lt -1/2
K^2+K+2=(K+1/2)^2 +7/4
\sqrt{K^2+K+2} \gt K+1/2
K-\sqrt{K^2+K+2}\lt K-(K+1/2)=-1/2
